*******************************
          Pywemil
 The Python Web-Mining Library
*******************************

Python Version :
  This library uses Python 3. All dependencies also use Python 3.

Licence :
  This Software is released under BSD license.

Mandatory Dependencies :
  Chardet [http://chardet.feedparser.org/]

Dependencies :
  Some dependencies are necessary to use extra-modules : tools, parsers. Pywemil Core can be used out of the box. To use tools and parsers, you may have to install following libraries :
  
  PyQt4 [http://www.riverbankcomputing.co.uk/software/pyqt/download]
  xlrd3 [http://pypi.python.org/pypi/xlrd3]
